headline: Regions Bank Names Andy Voress Head of Affordable Housing Investor Sales and Servicing
summary: BIRMINGHAM, Ala., November 20, 2025--Regions Bank on Thursday announced Andy Voress has joined Regions Affordable Housing as head of Investor Sales and Servicing.
